reviewText: Great combination of climbing videos.  Well worth the price.
I picked this up for my wife, she loved it. I enjoyed it as well and I'm a non-climber
This collection of video's is jaw dropping!!  I highly recommend this dvd.

Conrad, Sharma, Chin & Honnold make this film epic. Great story & love Honnolds triple!
Got this movie fast and left me with sweaty palms! Get some chalk-
